"2  carrots, peeled and julienned","1  small jicama (about 1 1/4 lbs.), peeled and julienned","1  large red bell pepper, cored and very thinly sliced","1/4  head red cabbage, cored and very thinly sliced","1/2  red onion, halved lengthwise and very thinly sliced lengthwise, rinsed, and patted dry","6 tablespoons olive oil","6 tablespoons unseasoned rice vinegar","3 tablespoons fresh lime juice","1 tablespoon minced cilantro leaves, plus more for garnish","1 teaspoon salt","1 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1 teaspoon sugar","1/2 teaspoon chili powder","1/2 teaspoon red chile flakes"